description: This file is a C source code file implementing parts of the CCSP CWMP Processor Object, including functions for engaging, canceling, setting up, closing the environment, handling timers, delivery of events, and transfer complete processing for TR-069 protocol operations.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoEngage(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,BOOL bRestart)
methods.description: Engages the CWMP processor, sets up environment, and spawns async connection task.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoCancel(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Cancels the CWMP processor, stops timers, and closes environment.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoSetupEnv(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,BOOL bRestart)
methods.description: Sets up environment including management server initialization, message bus registration, parameter cache, and configuration.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoCloseEnv(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Closes the operating environment, placeholder implementation.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoPeriodicTimerInvoke(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Handles timer expiration for periodic Inform; creates a session and adds an event for inform.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoScheduleTimerInvoke(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Handles scheduled Inform timer, creates an event with CommandKey.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoPendingInformTimerInvoke(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Handles pending inform timer, signals session to connect now.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoRedeliverEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Redelivers undelivered events such as TransferComplete, AutonomousTransferComplete, DUStateChangeComplete, etc.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoGetUndeliveredEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hWmpSession)
methods.description: Collects various undelivered events into a session.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoGetUndeliveredTcEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hWmpSession)
methods.description: Loads undelivered TransferComplete events from PSM into session.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoGetUndeliveredAtcEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hWmpSession)
methods.description: Loads undelivered AutonomousTransferComplete events from PSM.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoGetUndeliveredDscEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hWmpSession)
methods.description: Loads undelivered DUStateChangeComplete events from PSM.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoGetUndeliveredAdscEvents(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hWmpSession)
methods.description: Loads undelivered AutonomousDUStateChangeComplete events from PSM.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoSaveTransferComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,char * pCommandKey,ANSC_HANDLE hStartTime,ANSC_HANDLE hCompleteTime,BOOL bIsDownload,PCCSP_CWMP_FAULT pFault)
methods.description: Saves a TransferComplete event record into persistent storage (PSM).

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS ccspCwmppoLoadTransferCompleteTask(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Loads recorded transfer complete events from PSM and sends them out, then removes from storage.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoLoadTransferComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Initiates loading and sending out transfer complete events.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoLoadAutonomousTransferComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Loads and sends any stored AutonomousTransferComplete events, invoked to process undelivered events.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS ccspCwmppoLoadAutonomousTransferCompleteTask(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Loads undelivered AutonomousTransferComplete events from PSM , sends out notifications, deletes from PSM.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoSaveDUStateChangeComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hDsccReq)
methods.description: Saves DUStateChangeComplete event into PSM, including associated parameters.

methods.name: ccspCwmppoLoadDUStateChangeComplete
methods.description: Loads and sends DUStateChangeComplete events stored in PSM, including processing various parameters and timestamps.

methods.name: CcspCwmppoLoadDUStateChangeCompleteTask
methods.description: Processes pending DUStateChangeComplete events from PSM and sends to ACS.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoSaveAutonomousDUStateChangeComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hAdsccReq)
methods.description: Saves AutonomousDUStateChangeComplete events into PSM for later delivery.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoLoadAutonomousDUStateChangeComplete(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Triggers loading and sending of undelivered AutonomousDUStateChangeComplete events.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS ccspCwmppoLoadAutonomousDUStateChangeCompleteTask(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Loads, sends, and cleans up undelivered AutonomousDUStateChangeComplete events.

methods.name: CcspCwmppoDiscardUndeliverEvents
methods.description: Discards any undelivered events stored in PSM, including TransferComplete, AutonomousTransferComplete, DUStateChangeComplete, and others.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoLoadValueChanged(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Begins loading of undelivered value change events, spawning task to process them.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoLoadValueChangedTask(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Reads stored value change events from PSM and triggers the ValueChanged callback for each.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoSaveValueChanged(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,char * pParameterName)
methods.description: Stores a new value change event in PSM for a specific parameter.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS CcspCwmppoDiscardValueChanged(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,char * pParameterName)
methods.description: Removes pending value change events for a specific parameter from PSM.

methods.description: unavailable

methods.description: unavailable
